<PageLayout title="Folsom Psychology — Scheduling Automation | Emily Backes" description="In this UX case study, learn how I helped transform Folsom Psychology's business operations, cutting patient scheduling times in half." ogImage="/assets/cs/sage/662ad570421ba9e8a98b25bc_og-eb-logo.png" bodyBg="#333">
<div class="cs-port-root">
<section class="fs_hero__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_hero__container w-container"><div class="fs_hero__wrapper"><h1 data-w-id="81fe7aa5-df03-a19a-1041-c17cb4662ca9" class="fs_hero__headline">How I Helped Reduce Patient Scheduling Times In Half</h1><div data-w-id="fbc157d1-4132-58d8-3268-000a504fc87f" class="fs_hero__subheading">Folsom Psychology needed serious help; they operated a growing business on spreadsheets.</div></div><div class="hero_img__wrapper"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/662154f2ac3ac9579dc452c9_org_person.avif" loading="lazy" width="500" alt="Folsom Hero Image" class="hero_person"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/662154bd6e83300765ad24e7_org_lines.avif" loading="lazy" width="500" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 500px" alt="" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/662154bd6e83300765ad24e7_org_lines-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/662154bd6e83300765ad24e7_org_lines.avif 1000w" class="hero_strings"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/662154d4ab76974596989442_org_papers.avif" loading="lazy" width="500" data-w-id="9942ad06-7a25-c455-6505-3f77fe0f5f99" alt="How I Helped Reduce Patient Scheduling Times In Half" class="hero_paper"/></div></div></section><section class="fs_backstory__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_backstory__container w-container"><div class="fs_backstory__wrapper"><div class="fs_bs__content"><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10">Getting to know the client</strong></div><h2 class="fs_section__heading">Backstory of Folsom Psychology (FP)</h2><div class="fs_section___txt bs_sub_text">Folsom Psychology is a woman owned and operated practice providing imperative mental health services for Coloradoans. </div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_bs__detail">Their business has taken off in the last few years while their tools and processes struggle to keep up with the demand of their patient base. In order to continue growing the practice they also recognized the need to update their technology.</div><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-11">UX / UI SKILLSET LEVERAGED<br/></strong></div><div class="fs_pill__wrapper"><div data-w-id="e309176a-ab27-32d1-b1c6-c6aa6906a1e6" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">In-depth Research</div><div data-w-id="01af8ebd-8b70-00a7-4024-76cded3386d7" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">API Integration Research</div><div data-w-id="be4353d7-67ae-6db5-93f5-561ccd8164a9" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">User Interviews</div><div data-w-id="fa1f885f-0e3d-bb7b-646f-c8c12a0bae03" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">Complex User Flows</div><div data-w-id="d41b49c6-ccaf-cc88-8244-2e3277548257" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">Mid Fi Mockups</div><div data-w-id="67398b02-7a18-ae7a-6f4d-6b0e4e8e7dfd" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">High Fi Mockups</div><div data-w-id="8f412f4a-900a-ea81-cecc-fe5af529cd03" class="default_pill fs_tools__pill">UI Creation</div></div><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-13">UX / UI tools LEVERAGED<br/></strong></div><div class="ux_tools__wrapper"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/65ff30f1590d4325671e194a_Slack Logomark 1.svg" loading="lazy" height="40" alt="" data-w-id="96b90558-dc45-4f7a-9833-a3fe33ee0d17" class="ux_tools_logo"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/661df43fa3542c723f8b17df_zeplin_1.svg" loading="lazy" height="40" alt="" data-w-id="96b90558-dc45-4f7a-9833-a3fe33ee0d18" class="ux_tools_logo"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/65ff30f14bf5714c0727d94c_Google Calendar Logomark 1.svg" loading="lazy" height="40" alt="" data-w-id="96b90558-dc45-4f7a-9833-a3fe33ee0d19" class="ux_tools_logo"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/65ff2f932a7ab8b822cdf03e_Notion Logomark 1.svg" loading="lazy" height="40" alt="" data-w-id="96b90558-dc45-4f7a-9833-a3fe33ee0d1a" class="ux_tools_logo"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/65ff30f7b6d7ec1b27f59edb_Miro Logomark 1.svg" loading="lazy" height="40" alt="" data-w-id="96b90558-dc45-4f7a-9833-a3fe33ee0d1b" class="ux_tools_logo"/></div><div class="nda_clause nda_folsom">Note: Due to an on-going Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) with Bowtie &amp; our client, this project has been anonymized to &#x27;Folsom Psychology&#x27;. </div></div><div class="fs_bs__stat__wrapper"><div class="bs_stat__item"><div class="lottie-animation-18" data-w-id="adaa01da-c9a8-4ec5-33bd-77be5848f17e" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/66218e71cee5fa50f59ba335_wired-outline-18-location-pin_1.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1.8333333333333333" data-duration="4" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-78"><strong>Three office </strong>locations</div></div><div class="bs_stat__item"><div class="lottie-animation-17" data-w-id="4d5daf56-2842-e666-2ade-8cf523f29c97" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/66218e853f18a8b281020891_wired-outline-153-bar-chart.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1.5" data-duration="4" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-79">‍<strong>12 years in business</strong></div></div><div class="bs_stat__item"><div class="lottie-animation-16" data-w-id="8dcc21e9-0c34-fecb-446b-dc8493eceea7" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/66218ebfbb414d0622532c9a_wired-outline-955-demand.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1.5" data-duration="4" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-80">‍<strong class="bold-text-14"> 30+ practitioners</strong></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="fs_client__challenge__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_cc__container w-container"><div data-w-id="26c4af3b-e402-34e1-ab70-67196f454dad" class="fs_cc__wrapper"><div class="cc_content"><div class="fs_section__sub cc_subheading">real world problems</div><h2 class="fs_section__heading cc_heading"><strong class="bold-text-12">The Client Challenge</strong></h2><div class="fs_section___txt fs_cc__text cc_lg__txt">When FP approached us to build a platform, they already had several tools integrated into their practice. Despite these tools, many processes were updated weekly on <strong>6 different spread sheets</strong>.</div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_cc__text">One major opportunity for impact was matching a new patient with a provider. Folsom’s utmost concern is ensuring that the patient’s unique needs are matched to the best provider.</div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_cc__text">Starting from &quot;perfect&quot; and working backwards, I asked:<br/><br/><em>How can I reduce the cognitive load for Folsom&#x27;s admins during the matching phase? </em></div></div><div class="cc_image__wrapper"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/661eadc151f6189879e3b843_folsom_cognitive_2.avif" loading="lazy" width="Auto" height="400" alt="Client Challenge Cognitive Load" class="client-challenge-image"/></div></div></div></section><section class="fs_ux__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_ux__container w-container"><div class="fs_ux__wrapper"><div class="fs_ux__heading__wrapper"><div class="fs_section__sub">The ux process of discoery</div><h2 class="fs_section__heading"><strong class="bold-text-15">Finding User Friction Areas</strong></h2></div><div class="fs_ux__research__wrapper"><div class="div-block-124"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/6623059b20b23450f3a326e4_key_areas_of_ux.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="ux_key_area_img"/><div class="text-block-171">The client had a complex process and set of tools. <br/>I needed to make sure we captured their business <br/>as accurately as possible.</div></div><div class="fs_ux__key__areas__wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid grid-20"><div id="w-node-_796173e6-36b5-bdd6-beba-afb4630d0d2d-501d1bb6" data-w-id="796173e6-36b5-bdd6-beba-afb4630d0d2d" class="research_01"><div class="research_heading"><div class="lottie-animation-19" data-w-id="5638d399-f5e2-088e-2489-40b2361727d5" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/662302942878624e7d5544de_wired-outline-1422-polygon.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="3.5" data-duration="7" data-loading="eager"></div></div><div class="res_text__wrapper"><div class="text-block-81">API Research</div></div><div class="text-block-82">Performed extensive API comparison(s) with pre-existing  tools in a effort consolidate solutions.</div></div><div id="w-node-adaa1735-e807-b013-ac95-ceb2f342cdd7-501d1bb6" data-w-id="adaa1735-e807-b013-ac95-ceb2f342cdd7" class="research_01"><div class="research_heading"><div class="lottie-animation-19" data-w-id="adaa1735-e807-b013-ac95-ceb2f342cdd9" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/662302941a479f3b1b1d5995_wired-outline-1419-polyline.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="2.6666666666666665" data-duration="4.5" data-loading="eager"></div></div><div class="res_text__wrapper"><div class="text-block-81">Interviews </div></div><div class="text-block-82">Conducted 7 total interviews capturing the process for patient on-boarding , admin hiring, provider hiring, and claims  and billing.</div></div><div id="w-node-cba6fb26-ad6d-7fe1-fa7f-506250f9353f-501d1bb6" data-w-id="cba6fb26-ad6d-7fe1-fa7f-506250f9353f" class="research_01"><div class="research_heading"><div class="lottie-animation-19" data-w-id="cba6fb26-ad6d-7fe1-fa7f-506250f93541" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/66230294432ba73de156e487_wired-outline-1416-triangle.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="3.25" data-duration="5" data-loading="eager"></div></div><div class="res_text__wrapper"><div class="text-block-81">Data Models </div></div><div class="text-block-82">Generated visual representation of Folsom&#x27;s workflow and information architecture.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="fs_ux__solutions__wrapper"><div class="ux_img__wrapper"><img class="ux_callout__txt" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6622986d8d12e55330e27709_ux_7_call_out__textpng.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="e84011b6-931c-ff8f-22ab-d72f598e478d" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6622986d8d12e55330e27709_ux_7_call_out__textpng-p-500.avif 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622986d8d12e55330e27709_ux_7_call_out__textpng-p-800.avif 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622986d8d12e55330e27709_ux_7_call_out__textpng-p-1080.avif 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622986d8d12e55330e27709_ux_7_call_out__textpng.avif 2567w"/><img class="ux_callout_arrow" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6622984e297978b85cd33ded_ux_6_call_out__arrow.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="c01181f4-fcc6-4bae-c257-0b72fd61f250" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6622984e297978b85cd33ded_ux_6_call_out__arrow-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622984e297978b85cd33ded_ux_6_call_out__arrow-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622984e297978b85cd33ded_ux_6_call_out__arrow.avif 2567w"/><img class="ux_app1" src="/assets/cs/folsom/662295b0232829c9ed2f1720_ux_2_bowtie_app_1.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="66c42351-cd62-f121-71ef-012f93e505d2" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/662295b0232829c9ed2f1720_ux_2_bowtie_app_1-p-500.avif 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/662295b0232829c9ed2f1720_ux_2_bowtie_app_1-p-800.avif 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/662295b0232829c9ed2f1720_ux_2_bowtie_app_1-p-1080.avif 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/662295b0232829c9ed2f1720_ux_2_bowtie_app_1.avif 2567w"/><img class="ux_app2" src="/assets/cs/folsom/662297fe912fdc08dd6f8525_ux_3_bowtie_app_2.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="e19071e3-de19-7d61-0cae-7cde8191ac0a" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/662297fe912fdc08dd6f8525_ux_3_bowtie_app_2-p-500.avif 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/662297fe912fdc08dd6f8525_ux_3_bowtie_app_2-p-800.avif 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/662297fe912fdc08dd6f8525_ux_3_bowtie_app_2.avif 2567w"/><img class="ux_lg__circle" src="/assets/cs/folsom/662298108a5095c7567d62e9_ux_4_large_circle.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="708f9e42-1a85-43b2-b967-daef5532f465" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/662298108a5095c7567d62e9_ux_4_large_circle-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/662298108a5095c7567d62e9_ux_4_large_circle-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/662298108a5095c7567d62e9_ux_4_large_circle.avif 2567w"/><img class="ux_sm__circle" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6622983450774ab679e5483a_ux_5_small_circle.avif" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="e5fe7ab1-9eb8-34c9-7892-6a94b77f32e9" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6622983450774ab679e5483a_ux_5_small_circle-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622983450774ab679e5483a_ux_5_small_circle-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6622983450774ab679e5483a_ux_5_small_circle.avif 2567w"/><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/662295723785c5f6f8b36693_ux_1_bg.avif" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/662295723785c5f6f8b36693_ux_1_bg-p-500.avif 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/662295723785c5f6f8b36693_ux_1_bg.avif 2567w" alt="UX User Flow" class="ux_bg"/></div><div class="ux_sol__detail__wrapper"><div class="text-block-81">User Interviews</div><div data-w-id="a4ca66aa-f374-ff2f-2f48-748d824010eb" class="fs_section___txt fs_ux__txt">The practice owner (Jennifer) &amp; the practice manager (Katie)  sat down with me over <strong>five</strong> zoom calls to detail the patient user flow, <strong>resulting in 4 iterations</strong>. I needed to capture the entire process accurately. <br/><br/>Ultimately with budget and timeline in mind, I needed to pin-point where our proposed solution would make the most impact. </div></div></div><div class="fs_ux__findings"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/6622bd3feab773131eafab7a_key_findings.avif" loading="lazy" alt="" class="ux_key_findings_img"/><div class="w-layout-grid ux_sol__findings__grid"><div id="w-node-_0e7fc29e-f10c-7ce4-6e71-a0dcc5fbcfd7-501d1bb6" class="finding_items"><div class="lottie-animation-13" data-w-id="4338759f-e333-66f0-78ec-d916cf210772" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/661ec0cc6b36791469151d1e_fff_wired-outline-1387-page-view-column.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1" data-duration="4" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-70">Admin&#x27;s were flipping through<strong> 7 different software</strong> during one call.</div></div><div id="w-node-de3da655-76d6-004f-42a3-e575002ed6e5-501d1bb6" class="finding_items"><div class="lottie-animation-13" data-w-id="de3da655-76d6-004f-42a3-e575002ed6e6" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/661ebfacaa31dad84b16baa3_fff_wired-outline-45-clock-time.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="2" data-duration="4" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-68">The <strong>average</strong> call time for scheduling new patients:  <strong>20-30 minutes</strong>.</div></div><div id="w-node-e95d65a2-daba-b364-3c79-daf40eb358bd-501d1bb6" class="finding_items"><div class="lottie-animation-13" data-w-id="e95d65a2-daba-b364-3c79-daf40eb358be" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/66218d8033e92a70f6c5239e_wired-outline-1676-telephone-call-hand.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="3.3" data-duration="6" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="text-block-69">An average of <strong>15 patients remain</strong> on the call-back waitlist at any given time.</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="fs_sketch__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_ui__container w-container"><div class="fs_ui__wrapper"><div class="fs_ux__content__wrapper"><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10">from ux to ui</strong></div><h2 class="fs_section__heading">Diving Into Data Driven Product Design</h2><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text lg_txt">We already had a design system in place which gave me the freedom to dig into how the <strong>UX data</strong> could <strong>inform</strong> and <strong>shape</strong> the UI components.</div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text">I had three key areas of focus when making UI design decisions for FP, based on key findings during UX research. </div><div class="ui_list__wrapper"><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text ui_bulleted__list">1. Reduce the number of applications admins had to use.</div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text ui_bulleted__list">2. Reduce call times when scheduling patients.</div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text">3. Reduce admin call backlogs.</div></div><div class="fs_section___txt fs_ui__text">Where to even begin? I guess we can start with sketches.</div></div></div><div class="div-block-234"><div class="div-block-236"><div class="text-block-167">I sketch early &amp; often</div><div class="text-block-164"><strong>Sketches have low consequences. </strong>They allow me to think about the product layout without using any tools that will just add complexities to my decision making.<br/>‍<br/>The sketches below are a bit <strong>abstract</strong>, but I start with such low fidelity because I want to focus on key areas of design. <br/><br/>My sketches are generally never shared with the team, they are simply for me to test out layout &amp; structure.<br/><br/>I try to stay focused on shapes and structure, but you see how the color scheme palette is already a distraction?<br/></div></div><div class="div-block-235"><div><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/66689194bb3de7d98efd0d77_folsom_ui_graphic_1.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/66689194bb3de7d98efd0d77_folsom_ui_graphic_1-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689194bb3de7d98efd0d77_folsom_ui_graphic_1-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689194bb3de7d98efd0d77_folsom_ui_graphic_1.webp 1024w" alt=""/></div><div><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/666891bf5057d3f2189c2337_folsom_ui_graphic_2.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/666891bf5057d3f2189c2337_folsom_ui_graphic_2-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/666891bf5057d3f2189c2337_folsom_ui_graphic_2-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/666891bf5057d3f2189c2337_folsom_ui_graphic_2.webp 1024w" alt=""/></div></div><div class="div-block-239"><div class="div-block-240"><div class="text-block-168">From the client interviews I discovered that there were 10 main categories that admins used to sort and filter, so in the low fidelity mock-up <strong>I conceptualized 10 drop-down selections. </strong><br/><br/>Throughout iteration I discovered that providing a screen with <strong>10 drop downs was doing nothing to decrease the cognitive load, so I looked for another solution.<br/><br/></strong>We&#x27;ll call the sketch below, version 1.</div></div><div class="div-block-241"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown-p-1080.png 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown-p-1600.png 1600w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown-p-2000.png 2000w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c2b0ec64722eca532c5c_Folsom_Dropdown.webp 2041w" alt="Folsom Dropdown Idea" class="image-123"/></div></div><div class="div-block-243"><div class="div-block-245"><div class="text-block-169">Let&#x27;s call this one version 2. Mid-Fi testing showed that the three choices prior to search was confusing to users. <br/><br/>Closer to the final search bar the team and I agreed was the solution, but still needed to make changes. </div></div><div class="div-block-244"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/6669c4df9ba8ec69510f7413_Folsom_Search_Bar_1.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6669c4df9ba8ec69510f7413_Folsom_Search_Bar_1-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c4df9ba8ec69510f7413_Folsom_Search_Bar_1-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c4df9ba8ec69510f7413_Folsom_Search_Bar_1-p-1080.png 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6669c4df9ba8ec69510f7413_Folsom_Search_Bar_1.webp 1589w" alt=""/></div></div><div><div class="div-block-238"><div class="text-block-166">After several iterations and <strong>still not convinced that drop downs were the answer</strong>, I came up with with &quot;Smart Search&quot; as a solution to remove as much cognitive load from the admins.<br/><br/>The search bar would <strong>only need 3 specific criteria</strong> that the admins most often use to automatically generate the most relevant provider matches, internally.<br/><br/>Below are early sketches of the final search bar once the team and I decided to pivot away from the drop downs, we&#x27;ll call it version 3.</div></div><div class="div-block-237"><div><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c89dfee108c2e3eadb6_folsom_ui_graphic_3.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c89dfee108c2e3eadb6_folsom_ui_graphic_3-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c89dfee108c2e3eadb6_folsom_ui_graphic_3-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c89dfee108c2e3eadb6_folsom_ui_graphic_3.webp 1024w" alt=""/></div><div><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c89ec04c53cae16084e_folsom_ui_graphic_4.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c89ec04c53cae16084e_folsom_ui_graphic_4-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c89ec04c53cae16084e_folsom_ui_graphic_4-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c89ec04c53cae16084e_folsom_ui_graphic_4.webp 1024w" alt=""/></div><div><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c890a82c2aa996c34a9_folsom_ui_graphic_5.webp" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/66689c890a82c2aa996c34a9_folsom_ui_graphic_5-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c890a82c2aa996c34a9_folsom_ui_graphic_5-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/66689c890a82c2aa996c34a9_folsom_ui_graphic_5.webp 1024w" alt=""/></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="fs_screens__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_screens__container w-container"><div class="fs_screens__wrapper"><div class="div-block-246"><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10">getting to good, not perfect</strong></div><div class="text-block-170">From sketches to UI</div><div class="text-block-172">From sketch iterations to UI iterations. <br/>‍<br/>My philosophy is not to get it perfect the<br/>first round, but rather, iterate my way to &#x27;<strong>good</strong>&#x27;.<br/><br/><strong>Perfectionism is the enemy of productivity. </strong></div></div><div class="div-block-248"><div class="div-block-249"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter.webp" alt="Folsom Filter" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="8ce4e95f-a17d-7dca-ac58-87b952a400e5" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter-p-1080.png 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter-p-1600.png 1600w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c777c9b1fc797aa99f804_fs_filter.webp 1978w"/></div><div class="div-block-247"><div class="div-block-250"><img src="/assets/cs/folsom/666c77b790792c4eb550f062_cal.webp" alt="Folsom Calendar" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="cd2af625-cd14-1e61-0f54-81271ae2161e" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/666c77b790792c4eb550f062_cal-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77b790792c4eb550f062_cal-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77b790792c4eb550f062_cal-p-1080.png 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77b790792c4eb550f062_cal.webp 1402w"/></div><div class="div-block-251"><img class="image-124" src="/assets/cs/folsom/666c77cd9b1fc797aa9a41a3_fs_dropdown_small.webp" alt="Folsom Filter" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="fbfba11a-52a3-12af-7f05-60ef88d34275" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/666c77cd9b1fc797aa9a41a3_fs_dropdown_small-p-500.png 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77cd9b1fc797aa9a41a3_fs_dropdown_small-p-800.png 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77cd9b1fc797aa9a41a3_fs_dropdown_small-p-1080.png 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/666c77cd9b1fc797aa9a41a3_fs_dropdown_small.webp 1408w"/></div></div></div><div class="div-block-252"><img class="fs_screen__animate fs_screen_1" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7eff39a28d85a399e_match_1.webp" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="2272424e-00ec-6e28-00d4-d4d46d5dfc07" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7eff39a28d85a399e_match_1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7eff39a28d85a399e_match_1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7eff39a28d85a399e_match_1-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7eff39a28d85a399e_match_1.webp 1440w"/><img class="fs_screen__animate fs_screen_2" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7f9b90403a0032f50_match_2.webp" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="2c26e755-908c-6f73-e6f4-870cc71756db" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7f9b90403a0032f50_match_2-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7f9b90403a0032f50_match_2-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7f9b90403a0032f50_match_2-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbc7f9b90403a0032f50_match_2.webp 1440w"/><img class="fs_screen__animate fs_screen_3" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcb5d556ae423a97bbc_match_3.webp" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="3903df55-f1e4-77d4-2598-c8530e12f743" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcb5d556ae423a97bbc_match_3-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcb5d556ae423a97bbc_match_3-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcb5d556ae423a97bbc_match_3-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcb5d556ae423a97bbc_match_3.webp 1440w"/><img class="fs_screen__animate fs_screen_4" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcbb247f01b658a1f6e_match_4.webp" alt="" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="4951f3e7-f7aa-21eb-1183-66aa324d3e6d" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcbb247f01b658a1f6e_match_4-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcbb247f01b658a1f6e_match_4-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcbb247f01b658a1f6e_match_4-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcbb247f01b658a1f6e_match_4.webp 1440w"/><img class="fs_screen__animate fs_screen_5" src="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcd56051415b2de3981_match_5.webp" alt="Folsom Smart Search" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="d09ccf55-5686-e52e-381d-5599bdc26df5" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcd56051415b2de3981_match_5-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcd56051415b2de3981_match_5-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcd56051415b2de3981_match_5-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/cs/folsom/6668cbcd56051415b2de3981_match_5.webp 1440w"/></div></div></div></section><section class="fs_outcome__section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer fs_outcome__container w-container"><div class="fs_outcome__wrapper"><div><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10">where the rubber meets the road</strong></div><h2 class="fs_section__heading">Challenges &amp; Outcomes</h2></div><div data-w-id="198f8ddc-8f8a-cc4a-af65-9dfa7af00945" class="div-block-119"><div class="div-block-120"><div class="text-block-74">User Testing proved that the ability for the AC&#x27;s to see the best-ranked provider with the most availability was an imperative component to <strong>reducing cognitive load</strong>. </div><div class="text-block-74 md_txt">Instead of flipping between multiple programs and screens, they could focus all of their attention on the conversation with the patient. </div></div><div class="fs_outcome__stat__wrapper"><div class="stat_block"><p class="sol_stat_hdg">4</p><div class="text-block-72">Apps replaced by our solution</div></div><div class="stat_block"><p class="sol_stat_hdg">18</p><div class="text-block-71">Avg. call reduction time in minutes</div></div><div class="stat_block sol_btm_stat"><p class="sol_stat_hdg">10</p><div class="text-block-73">Avg. anxious patients removed from the call-back list</div></div></div></div><div class="div-block-122"><div data-w-id="b8ae8849-7a9f-10f7-2750-abe24517607f" class="div-block-123 project_chal"><div class="lottie-animation-14" data-w-id="8c0b23dd-9f45-63fd-80c7-9e72a44f48bb" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/6620950d5b29d8a856386d2d_ef9_wired-outline-1534-paper-boat.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="3" data-duration="5" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10 chal_subh_txt">project challenges</strong></div><div class="text-block-76">Midway through designing the provider match page, we realized there was a key filtering section <strong>missing</strong> from the design in the data model. This created a fairly significant design change across multiple screens.</div></div><div data-w-id="571a5f06-c928-052f-db96-d0c3a985796d" class="div-block-123 project_changes"><div class="lottie-animation-15" data-w-id="76f936d2-c643-cd19-c088-4ac8640061f8" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cs/folsom/662095cdd19641ced6c38277_ef9_wired-outline-12-layers.json" data-loop="1" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1.5" data-duration="3" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="fs_section__sub"><strong class="bold-text-10 changes_subh_txt">project changes</strong></div><div class="text-block-77">Migrating the project design system from <strong>Sketch</strong> to <strong>Figma</strong>, was a major change in the process. I spent a lot of effort cleaning the design system, once in Figma. The new design tool coupled with conversion issues was a major challenge.</div></div></div></div></div></section>
</div>

